Steam for BitlBee is a plugin for the Steam chat protocol.

Please note, this plugin is still under development.

Usage:
  ; account add steam <username> <password>
  ; account <acc> set authcode <code>

Building and Installing:
  $ git clone https://github.com/jgeboski/bumblebee-steam.git
  $ cd bumblebee-steam
  $ autoreconf -fi
  $ ./configure
  $ make
  $ make install

Resources:
  - API Dump:    http://pastebin.com/qsX36TMT
  - SteamWebAPI: https://github.com/Overv/SteamWebAPI
  - Valve Wiki:  https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Steam_Web_API
